data.description: Immaculate Three-Story Luxury Townhome with an elevator tucked away in the Overlook at Sixes Community. The Terrace Level is finished making the perfect in-law, guest, or teen suite with a large media/theatre room, guest bedroom, full bathroom, and a walk-out covered patio and grilling area. This home is steps away from the pristine fairways of the Bridgemill Golf Course and Athletic Club which offers athletic, golf, and tennis memberships. Conveniently located near local attractions such as Lake Allatoona, The Outlets of Atlanta in Woodstock, restaurants, and more. This well-maintained townhome boasts gleaming hardwood flooring, 10ft ceilings with architectural arches on the main level, exquisite crown molding and trim, and a plethora of high-end finishes throughout the home. The open-concept floorplan flows seamlessly from the kitchen to the Butler’s Pantry area with lots of room for storage and dining set-up. The formal dining room showcases the elegantly coffered ceilings and is ideal for hosting large dinner parties. The impressive chef’s kitchen features custom cabinetry, stone countertops, five burner gas cooktop, double ovens, dual pantries, and a large center island that is complemented by high-end stainless-steel appliances. The kitchen flows gracefully into the spacious great room with a stone-stacked gas fireplace with a wine/coffee bar and easy access to the enclosed deck with can lights and a ceiling fan making it a very warm and inviting place to entertain your guests. There is also a guest bedroom with a full bath and walk-in closet on the main level. Use the elevator to access the third level and the owner’s suite. The spacious owner suite awaits you upstairs complete with trey ceilings, a sitting area, a custom-built walk-in closet, separate his/her vanities, a soaking tub, and a tiled shower with a seating bench. An additional bedroom, full bath, loft area, and a laundry room on the third floor.
